    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and meticulously kept, this is the one. Can't wait for you to take it for a spin!",
