    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in pristine, showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero scratches, dings, or rock chips, recently enhanced by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the interior retains its original factory freshness. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained ahead of schedule at authorized service centers. We have a complete binder of service records, all original keys, and the original window sticker. This is a collector-grade specimen that drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
